### SendMultipleEmbeds(embeds)

Sends multiple embeds in a single message (up to 10 embeds).

**Parameters:**
- `embeds` (array, required): Array of embed tables

**Returns:**
- `boolean`: true if queued successfully, false on error

**Example:**
```lua
local embeds = {
    {
        title = "üìà Player Stats",
        color = 0x00ff00,
        fields = {{name = "Active Players", value = "15", inline = true}}
    },
    {
        title = "‚ö†Ô∏è Server Health",
        color = 0xffaa00,
        fields = {{name = "Memory Usage", value = "85%", inline = true}}
    }
}

webhook:SendMultipleEmbeds(embeds)
```

**Notes:**
- Limited to 10 embeds per Discord message
- Each embed is individually sanitized
- Useful for dashboard-style reports

### Simple Text Messages

```lua
-- Basic message
webhook:SendMessage("üéÆ Server has started successfully!")

-- Message with custom override
webhook:SendMessage("üì¢ Special announcement from admin!", {
    username = "üì¢ Admin Bot",
    avatar_url = "https://cdn.discordapp.com/avatars/123/special-avatar.png"
})
```

### Rich Embed Examples

```lua
-- Game statistics embed
webhook:SendEmbed({
    title = "üèÜ Game Statistics",
    description = "Current server statistics and information",
    color = 0x0099ff,
    fields = {
        {name = "üë• Players Online", value = tostring(#game.Players:GetPlayers()), inline = true},
        {name = "‚è∞ Server Uptime", value = "2 hours 15 minutes", inline = true},
        {name = "üåç Region", value = "US-East", inline = true},
        {name = "üìä Performance", value = "Excellent", inline = false}
    },
    thumbnail = {
        url = "https://www.roblox.com/asset-thumbnail/image?assetId=123456789&width=420&height=420"
    },
    footer = {
        text = "Automated Report"
    },
    timestamp = os.date("!%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ")
})
```

### Multiple Embeds in One Message

```lua
local embeds = {
    {
        title = "üìà Player Stats",
        color = 0x00ff00,
        fields = {{name = "Active Players", value = "15", inline = true}}
    },
    {
